Also, the Makefile in the repository specifically excludes the file tensorflow/core/lib/db/sqlite.cc from the build, so is it possible that you're using a different Makefile?

body:
What is the source of the `build_all_ios_ssd.sh` script? (I haven't been able to find that in the TensorFlow repository.)

Also, the [`Makefile` in the repository ](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/d76ab0431f30ed7ca283b2e343fefb7b4cb9e9f5/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/Makefile)specifically excludes the file `tensorflow/core/lib/db/sqlite.cc` from the build, so is it possible that you're using a different `Makefile`?
